title: Hear New Animal Collective Song “Kinda Bonkers” From Forthcoming The Painters EP
text: Animal Collective played a DJ set in San Francisco on Thursday night, and they used the opportunity to debut a new song. According to Shazam , it's called "Kinda Bonkers" and comes from a forthcoming EP entitled The Painters, presumably a companion to last year's Painting With .
